Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As times change, difficult\Ncases increase in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's case involves three siblings!\NMysteries upon mysteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the\Nsingle truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.45,0:00:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Hotta Siblings Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:02:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! And I came all this way\Nbecause he said it was a big incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've just taken the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! I'm not gonna search\Nfor some lousy missing iguana!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds perfect for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What seems to be the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My car broke down on me.\NCould I ask for a lift to my villa up ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll compensate you, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be glad to give you a lift!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. My name is Hotta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hotta Industries!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You run that huge corporation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yamauchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My car broke down.\NThese folks gave me a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? I'm Yamauchi,\Nthe caretaker of this villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing! I'm sure\Nhe would've done the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Koichi and\Nthe others already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Everyone is worried\Nbecause you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder. I bet they hope\NI died in an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}.\NTonight is my birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to invite you, as thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind if I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't arrive on time,\NFather, so we were worried
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you had gotten in an\Naccident along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Hotta Industries is\Nnothing without you, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For sure! The company needs you\Nto stay well for a long time to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chateau Petrus, 1979.\NFrom Koichi-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Is that expensive wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Eye-poppingly expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the king of red wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let us toast\Nto Father's 58th birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you drink first, big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just figured it wouldn't be\Nfunny if there was poison in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude, Ryoji-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The overseas branch has taken\Nbig hits because of your poor forecasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I hear you're going to be\Ndismissed and sent to a subsidiary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're suggesting I'm\Nplanning to kill Father over that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you've racked up some\Nheavy-duty gambling debts lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had just about enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see my brothers are as close as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Eldest Daughter- Hotta Fumiko (30)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a harsh hello,\Nafter sending an invitation yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We severed all ties five years ago!\NI'd never send you an invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see your face! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who called\Nme here to tell me something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to say to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight was supposed\Nto be a feast, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what happened between\NHotta-{\i1}san {\i0}and Fumiko-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question. I've only been\Ntheir caretaker for two years,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't know\Nwhat happened long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whiskey, huh?\NWhose present is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What the--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I can assume\Na bomb was planted in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out! Please wait outside\Nuntil the police arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's greatest detective,\NMori Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Kogoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The famous detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was dynamite...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't smell like dynamite to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to butt in again, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has wood and glass fragments in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid kid! Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a whiskey display box!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! The glass stuck\Nin him is from a bottle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bomb was inside the whiskey box!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why there are\Nfragments all over Hotta-{\i1}san{\i0}'s body!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to tell me!\NI realized that long before you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dirt? What's it doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Yamauchi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says the phone is out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone here holds a grudge\Nagainst Father... it's you, Fumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You hadn't spoken in five years!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly showing up now without\Nan invitation is undeniably strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I did hate him.\NEnough to want to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't do it.\NThough I do thank whoever did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume you all feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What horrible siblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are the phone lines?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been cut\Nby a knife or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A knife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bomb was planted\Ninside a whiskey box.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? T-This display box was--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You recognize it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it was a present\NRyoji-{\i1}sama {\i0}gave to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember because\NI took it to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R- Ryoji did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, where is Ryoji-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran off...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ryoji-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't gotten far,\Nif he left his car behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Does that mean\Nhe's still lurking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?! It's been slashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}. What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably best\Nto leave in our cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All four of these\Ncars have slashed tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Does that mean\Nwe can't leave this villa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoji did this. There's\Nrubber stuck on his knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't drive, so we took a limo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:11:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's my car. But it's broken\Nand hardly in a usable state...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, if Ryoji-{\i1}san {\i0}is the killer,\Nwhy would he slash his own tires?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious? If his tires\Nwere the only ones not slashed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the police would suspect\Nhim right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. He would still\Nbe suspected right off the bat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if his whiskey exploded\Nand he disappeared right after!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoji-{\i1}san{\i0} didn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the killer's goal was actually\Nto trap everyone inside this villa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...something else might happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any event, Ryoji-{\i1}san\N{\i0}is still lurking around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to stay\Ntogether and not go off alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that! I'm going back to my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, right after I warn her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us all go back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}. I'll try to fix my car...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be extremely careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumiko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s pendant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumiko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet! I'm busy right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, little boy. This is\Nthe most important thing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died, five years ago. Suicide--\Nno, it was more like murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:13:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Hotta Kosaku, my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I left.\NI couldn't forgive my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry. I guess there's\Nno point in telling this to a little kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumiko-{\i1}san {\i0}held a\Ngrudge against Hotta-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But did she have a chance to\Nplant the bomb in the whiskey box?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:34.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Chemical Fertilizer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chemical fertilizer!\NCould that bomb have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:47.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sulfur
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sulfur and chemicals!\NAnd that chemical fertilizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it!\NThat person is the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person is--!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:14:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Oh, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That car sure is old!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first one I ever designed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a car designer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, until five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I quit after something happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen\Na car like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's an old-style car,\Nbut it has an airbag...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0},\Ncould you go get Fumiko-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get the police. Everyone feels\Nuneasy with just Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the caretaker. I have\Na responsibility to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, time for food!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably off playing somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a lost cause. I'll go find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My food...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be shocked.\NThis photograph was in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went into my\Nroom without permission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found something\Ninteresting in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sulfur and other chemicals,\Nhidden inside a cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The explosive wasn't dynamite.\NIt was a homemade bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,made of chemical fertilizer,\Nsulfur, and other chemicals!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make a bomb out of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If mixed properly, it can produce\Nan explosive as powerful as dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! Why would I want\Nto kill the master of the house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:16:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This incident was entirely to\Navenge the person in that photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotta-{\i1}san {\i0}drove him\Nto suicide five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he was your son,\NYamauchi-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who\Ntook Ryoji-{\i1}san{\i0}'s whiskey
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and delivered it\Nto Hotta-{\i1}san{\i0}'s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when you placed the\Nhomemade explosive inside the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an igniter under the lid,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and easily-ignited\Nphosphorous in the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was basically like striking a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't meant\Nto be a perfect crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you needed to\Ndistance yourself from suspicion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until your next crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His next crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumiko-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}.\NIt is just as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son Kentaro was an extraordinary\Npianist with a bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had dated a girl for a long time,\Nbut because of his paltry income,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was unable to propose to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But five years ago, he won a\Ncompetition and finally earned appraisal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Kentaro\Nproposed to her. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the woman's father--\NHotta-{\i1}san-{\i0}- was against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So that woman was Fumiko-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kentaro met with Hotta to\Nget permission to marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hotta not only refused,\Nbut he ruined Kentaro's fingers as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:18:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The piano was Kentaro's life!\NAnd he had it stolen away forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, the woman ran off,\Nleaving him behind devastated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the poor boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon learning all of this after his funeral,\NI was shocked to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that as a company man,\NI had known nothing about my own son...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you\Ndecided to get revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. After quitting the company,\NI investigated Hotta
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and became his caretaker to\Nfind a chance to exact revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Fumiko had left the family,\Nand it took me two years to locate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you chose Hotta-{\i1}san{\i0}'s\Nbirthday party as the stage for revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sent Fumiko-{\i1}san {\i0}an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Now I will have no regrets in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Fumiko-{\i1}san {\i0}is safe\Nand sound in the car--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I got her to step\Ninto that car, my revenge succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a trap in the car, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The airbag is set to go off\Nwhen she steps hard on the brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we speak, she's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't know anything, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think Fumiko-{\i1}san\N{\i0}is still single, after all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because even now,\Nshe continues to love Kentaro-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absurd! A rude woman disowned\Nby her father would never do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't disowned!\NShe left on her own!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't forgive her father\Nfor what he did to Kentaro-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie! It's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She abandoned Kentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Fumiko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A treasure chest filled with\Nher memories with Kentaro-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and her feelings for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumiko-{\i1}san {\i0}always\Nwears it at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, Kentaro-{\i1}san {\i0}is the\Ndearest person to her, Yamauchi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've killed the person\Nwho loved my son that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:21:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumiko-{\i1}san{\i0}! Didn't the airbag deploy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Mori-{\i1}san {\i0}had Conan-{\i1}kun\N{\i0}tell me to come back right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumiko-{\i1}san{\i0}... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hated my father, too.\NEnough to want to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't forgive\NKentaro-{\i1}san{\i0}, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left me all alone...\NAnd drove his own father to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really is sinful...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoji-{\i1}san {\i0}had been\Nlocked up in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Where did everyone go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm hungry. Oh, that's right!\NWe're about to have breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamauchi-{\i1}san{\i0}! Breakfast, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.20,0:23:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry I could die!\NAnything'll do, just please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.79,0:23:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamauchi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.52,0:24:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange!\NSomething isn't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.62,0:24:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.79,0:24:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to wash makeup\Noff before applying a face pack!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.32,0:24:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's it! That person\Nreally is the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.09,0:24:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.65,0:24:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Face Pack Murder Case."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.98,0:24:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.97,0:24:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lipstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.75,0:24:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode's case is really unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.97,0:24:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.30,0:24:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
